1. How do I configure lighttpd?
http://redmine.lighttpd.net/projects/lighttpd/wiki/TutorialConfiguration

server.document-root = "/var/www/servers/www.example.org/pages/" 

server.port = 3000

mimetype.assign = (
  ".html" => "text/html", 
  ".txt" => "text/plain",
  ".jpg" => "image/jpeg",
  ".png" => "image/png" 
)
